#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>One</para>"
msgstr "<para>Eden</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmahjongg; is a fun board game created after the famous oriental game of "
"Mahjong (from Chinese <foreignphrase lang=\"zh\">麻將</foreignphrase>). "
"Unlike the original however, &kmahjongg; is a tile matching game for one "
"player, a variation usually known as Mahjong Solitaire."
msgstr ""
"&kmahjongg; je zabavna družabna igra, ustvarjena po znani orientalski igri "
"Mahjong (iz kitajščine <foreignphrase lang=\"zh\">麻將</foreignphrase>). Za "
"razliko od izvirnika pa &kmahjongg; je igra ujemanja ploščic za enega "
"igralca, različica, običajno znana kot Mahjong Solitaire."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &kmahjongg; the tiles are scrambled and stacked on top of each other to "
"resemble a certain shape. The player is then expected to remove all the "
"tiles off the game board by locating each tile's matching pair."
msgstr ""
"V &kmahjongg; ploščice so premešane in zložene ena na drugo, da so podobne "
"določeni obliki. Od igralca se nato pričakuje, da odstrani vse ploščice z "
"igralne plošče tako, da poišče ujemajoči se par za vsako ploščico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove all tiles from the game board by locating each tile's matching pair "
"as fast as possible."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite vse ploščice z igralne plošče tako, da čim hitreje poiščete "
"ujemajoči se par vsake ploščice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmahjongg; will load a default layout automatically once you start the game "
"and you can start playing right away."
msgstr ""
"&kmahjongg; bo samodejno naložil privzeto postavitev, ko začnete igro in "
"lahko začnete igrati takoj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73 index.docbook:77 index.docbook:192 index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Opomba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game timer will start immediately if the game is started."
msgstr "Časovnik igre se bo začel takoj, ko se igra začne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should carefully study the stack of tiles laid out on the game board and "
"find two tiles matching exactly. When you have found such a pair use your "
"mouse to select these."
msgstr ""
"Pazljivo preučite kup ploščic, ki so postavljene na igralno ploščo, in "
"poiščite dve ploščici, ki se popolnoma ujemata. Ko najdete tak par, jih z "
"miško izberite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bear in mind that you can only select the tiles which are <quote>Open</"
"quote>. Tiles are considered <quote>Blocked</quote> when they are positioned "
"behind other tiles, or when both the right and left sides of the tile are "
"filled by others. If at least one of the lateral sides is empty then the "
"tile is considered <quote>Open</quote>, and can be removed."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko izberete samo ploščice, ki so <quote>Odprte</quote>. "
"Ploščice se štejejo za <quote>blokirane</quote>, če so postavljene za "
"drugimi ploščicami ali ko so desno in levo stran ploščice zapolnjene z "
"drugimi. Če je vsaj ena od stranskih strani prazna, se ploščica šteje za "
"<quote>Odprto</quote> in jo je mogoče odstraniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have selected the right pair of tiles they will vanish off the game "
"board, thus revealing the tiles previously located underneath, and opening "
"the tiles adjacent to them."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete pravi par ploščic, bodo izginile z igralne plošče in tako "
"razkrile ploščice, ki so bile prej pod njimi, ter odprle ploščice, ki mejijo "
"nanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Find as many matches as possible to remove all the tiles from the game board."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite čim več zadetkov, da odstranite vse ploščice z igralne plošče."

