msgid "A quick explanation of the parts of the game screen."
msgstr "Hitra razlaga delov igralnega zaslona."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Screen"
msgstr "Igralni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Game screen is in the center of the screen and is the largest section of "
"the window. The background is populated with the game tiles."
msgstr ""
"Igralni zaslon je na sredini zaslona in je največji del okna. Ozadje je "
"poseljeno s ploščicami igre."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Vrstica stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar is located at the bottom of the screen, and contains four "
"panes. The first pane displays the game timer, which keeps track of the "
"elapsed time from the start of the game until the game is finished. The "
"second pane lists the removed/total tiles and the number of matching tiles "
"that have free sides. The third pane gives the sequence number of the game "
"you are playing and the last pane lets the player know when the game is "
"ready."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica stanja se nahaja na dnu zaslona in vsebuje štiri podokna. V prvem "
"podoknu je prikazan časovnik igre, ki beleži čas, ki je pretekel od začetka "
"igre do konca igre. V drugem podoknu je seznam odstranjenih/skupnih ploščic "
"in število ujemajočih se ploščic, ki imajo proste stranice. Tretje podokno "
"prikazuje zaporedno številko igre, ki jo igrate, zadnje podokno pa igralcu "
"sporoči, kdaj je igra pripravljena."

