#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of tiles on a &kmahjongg; board layout can differ from the number "
"of tiles in the standard Mahjong tile set. That means that the number of "
"occurrences of tiles of the same type can also differ from the number stated "
"in the table above."
msgstr ""
"Število ploščic na postavitvi plošče &kmahjongg; se lahko razlikuje od "
"števila ploščic v standardnem nizu ploščic Mahjong. To pomeni, da se lahko "
"število pojavitev ploščic istega tipa razlikuje tudi od števila, navedenega "
"v zgornji tabeli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only the <quote>open</quote> tiles can be selected."
msgstr "Izberete lahko samo <quote>odprte</quote> ploščice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Open</quote> tile is the tile which has one of the tile's lateral "
"sides open, meaning that no other tiles are located immediately next to it."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Odprta</quote> ploščica je ploščica, pri kateri je ena od stranskih "
"strani ploščice odprta, kar pomeni, da tik ob njej ni drugih ploščic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only when matching, open tiles can be removed from the game board."
msgstr "Odprte ploščice je mogoče odstraniti z igralne plošče le pri ujemanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matching tiles are those where the face pictograms match."
msgstr ""
"Ujemajoče se ploščice so tiste, pri katerih se piktogrami obrazov ujemajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are exceptions to this rule! In the traditional game of Mahjong each "
"tile has a matching one except for the <quote>Flowers</quote> and "
"<quote>Seasons</quote> tiles."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo izjeme od tega pravila! V tradicionalni igri Mahjong ima vsaka "
"ploščica ujemajočo se ploščico, razen ploščic <quote>Rože</quote> in "
"<quote>Letni časi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Flowers</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"Ploščice <quote>Rože</quote> v kompletu nimajo dvojnikov in jih je mogoče "
"povezati neposredno med seboj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Seasons</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"Ploščice <quote>Letni časi</quote> v kompletu nimajo dvojnikov in jih je "
"mogoče povezati neposredno med seboj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not every &kmahjongg; game can be finished. Sometimes the tiles are mixed in "
"such a way that it may not be possible to find all the matches. This problem "
"can be avoided. Please refer to <link linkend=\"general-options\">this "
"section</link> of the configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ni vsaka igra &kmahjongg; lahko končana. Včasih so ploščice pomešane tako, "
"da morda ni mogoče najti vseh ujemanj. Tej težavi se je mogoče izogniti. "
"Oglejte si <link linkend=\"general-options\">ta razdelek</link> "
"konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be eligible for a place amongst the high scores the player has to "
"complete a game instance within the shortest period of time possible."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bil igralec upravičen do mesta med najboljšimi rezultati, mora "
"dokončati primer igre v najkrajšem možnem času."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the player uses the <quote>Hint</quote> feature the record will not be "
"considered as a high score."
msgstr ""
"Če igralec uporablja funkcijo <quote>Namig</quote>, zapis ne bo upoštevan "
"kot visok rezultat."

