msgstr "<guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naključno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Shuffles the tiles</action> on the board."
msgstr "<action>Premeša ploščice</action> na plošči."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>G</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Rotate View Clockwise</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>G</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zasukaj pogled v smeri urinega kazalca</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Rotates</action> the tile viewing angle clockwise."
msgstr "<action>Zavrti</action> vidni kot ploščice v smeri urinega kazalca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Rotate View Counterclockwise</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zavrti pogled v nasprotni smeri urnega kazalca</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Rotates</action> the tile viewing angle counter clockwise."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zavrti</action> vidni kot ploščice v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kmahjongg; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kmahjongg; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the way &kmahjongg; looks use the <link linkend=\"menu"
"\">menubar</link> to open the <link linkend=\"configuration\">configuration "
"utility</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če želite spremeniti način videza &kmahjongg; uporabite <link linkend="
"\"menu\">menijsko vrstico</link>, da odprete <link linkend=\"configuration"
"\">pripomoček za konfiguracijo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not feature a keyboard play mode yet."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra še ne vsebuje načina igranja s tipkovnico."

